Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:22.29,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,This is the enemy's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:26.25,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Pleiades that thing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:32.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:34.92,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,it looks like it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:37.80,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,With its limbs having degenerated \Nto such a short length,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:43.06,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,it wouldn't be able to get any food, \Nlet alone move on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.18,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:46.06,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to strike, \Nyou should do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:49.82,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to blow it up \Nwith plastic explosives,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.82,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,but my backpack went down the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:55.07,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's only one way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:01:00.41,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to fight one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:02.21,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,I shall take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:04.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Your strength alone won't be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:07.53,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.17,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:51.93,Bullet_Ep_Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,425)}#12 Crisis Point
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.36,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuro Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.19,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Endless...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.48,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...Scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.38,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.50,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! The wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:42.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:12.89,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Aldebaran...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:30.83,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.67,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Aldebaran and the \Nothers have started to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:37.94,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Move?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:42.65,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:53.73,Bullet_Italics,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.14,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Seitenshi-sama, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.11,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I defeated Pleiades!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.80,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can use missiles and fighter jets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:04.11,Bullet_Italics,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. We will commence fire support.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:24.19,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Good... Now if they'll just \Ncontinue to disperse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.69,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,That's Aldebaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:50.78,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.34,Bullet_Flashback,gado,0000,0000,0000,,Aldebaran is immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.71,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,That's... impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.99,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:25.13,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:27.70,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you leave without saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.49,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.15,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:32.91,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:35.04,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:38.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I'm injured there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.21,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:43.76,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,You took too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:47.75,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness, you're all safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:51.02,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun... no, Leader Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.54,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Gado
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.51,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,has died in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.77,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with article 40 \Nof the civil officer manual,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:03.15,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,the officer with the next \Nhighest rank assumes command.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.42,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.03,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Lead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:22.35,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hate you, Gado.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.68,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Why, there you are, my comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.00,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:41.51,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,He saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:42.77,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Saved you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:46.80,Bullet_Main,civ,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him kill one of our \Ncomrades in the tent village!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.95,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,They decided to pick a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.53,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I merely gave them the fight they sought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.78,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you, Enju!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.91,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cut each other, Enju!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.77,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:04.38,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the enemy of all \Nof us civil officers, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:07.10,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, can I cut them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:09.13,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,You may kill half of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:12.22,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! This isn't the time to argue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:15.21,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Our common enemy is the Gastrea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:17.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to fight with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:20.36,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,think of a way to defeat as \Nmany Gastrea as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:27.23,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be keeping close observation of \Nyour capability as a commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.80,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:35.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:39.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Shoma-nii, where's Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:57.72,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Midori was trying to save an \NInitiator she didn't know....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:00.08,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,And then the Gastrea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.66,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,A neurotoxin stole her ability to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.30,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,and the Gastrea virus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:07.52,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,was injected into her continually \Nuntil I managed to save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.95,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,According to Sumire-sensei's examination,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:13.31,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,her corrosion rate is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:17.28,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, kill that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:23.95,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,You once fought me for the sake \Nof maintaining order in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.41,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,You won that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.53,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,This is the world that you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.42,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,You must make amends with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.02,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.68,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,I have a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.43,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,Please grasp a finger of your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.94,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,Are you touching my thumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:55.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:01.35,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't cheat, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:02.70,Bullet_Main,rsen,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:10.71,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,Because of my ears, \NI was never needed by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:12.95,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,Not even my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:17.86,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,But then Shoma-san needed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.05,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,And so did you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:23.79,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that'll make Shoma-nii and me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:26.31,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,is you getting better as soon as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:30.44,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,I smell confusion from you, Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.73,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Confusion has a smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:36.31,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,It's sort of intuitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:41.68,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,Also, concerning Tendo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:42.77,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Kisara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:46.78,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,I detect a very strong smell \Nof destruction from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:50.75,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,She is most likely very easily \Ninfluenced by the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:53.57,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.35,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,If you're the commander, Leader Satomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:11:00.26,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'll do okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:01.74,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Midori...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.94,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:05.72,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.67,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.77,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,To the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.77,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,You don't intend to follow me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:16.88,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.78,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:25.78,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,I might... take a little while in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:27.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:41.41,Bullet_Main,peeps,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:41.41,Bullet_Main,peeps,0000,0000,0000,,Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.55,Bullet_Main,some,0000,0000,0000,,Midori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:43.55,Bullet_Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:46.14,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:54.82,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Shoma-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.16,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Midori
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:14.73,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't want to burden \Neveryone in the adjuvant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:18.22,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi, let's just say that Midori ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:19.99,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,This will just upset everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.52,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Midori and I were a lot alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:33.77,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,We were both empty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.49,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and our contract was pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.19,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,to remedy each other's loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:42.75,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi, I didn't quit the Tendo Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:44.78,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,I was excommunicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.45,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:51.70,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,That was a technique that I modified.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:55.36,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,But destroying the enemy from the inside
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:58.35,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't a part of the Tendo Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:00.21,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Our master didn't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:04.56,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,That's also why I became a civil officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:12.11,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,I should have been there to finish her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.45,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,I was her partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:18.30,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Shoma-nii...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:20.70,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who killed Midori are the Gastrea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:25.21,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to mourn her death,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.28,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,swear to me that you'll defeat Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:32.08,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Stand, Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:37.60,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do it, \Neven more brutal deaths await.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:42.55,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop the Tokyo Area from \Ndrowning in a sea of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.26,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.05,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,You have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:56.92,Bullet_Main,civ a,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.72,Bullet_Main,civ b,0000,0000,0000,,That's Commander Gado's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:03.90,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Satomi Rentaro, and I will \Nbe taking over as commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:10.61,Bullet_Main,civ c,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The Tokyo Area's done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.16,Bullet_Main,civ c,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.26,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.38,Bullet_Main,civ c,0000,0000,0000,,What? You wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.95,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone else have any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.93,Bullet_Main,civ b,0000,0000,0000,,Chikaze, kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.69,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,If you move even a little, \Nyour head's gonna fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,What brought this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:46.25,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the ending I wanted, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:50.24,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! Anyone who tries to run,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.28,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,or threatens the peace of the \Ngroup will be eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:55.54,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not as kind as Gado was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:57.79,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,You're going too far, Satomi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.44,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was trembling in fear of the Gastrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:07.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, they won't be able to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:10.65,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, from now on, \NI'll be the one they fear
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.43,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of the Gastrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:16.55,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,But... then they'll curse you, and hate you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:20.34,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Then no one will be on your side, Satomi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:23.19,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't need anyone... At least for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.16,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:31.12,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the whole world turns against you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:34.03,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.66,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:39.50,Bullet_Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the actions of a dictator.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:42.31,Bullet_Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,You are not meant to be a commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:44.19,Bullet_Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Nagamasa-sama would have been more—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.50,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Gado is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.02,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:52.80,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't we lose twice because \Nhis methods were wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.89,Bullet_Main,girlie,0000,0000,0000,,You dare ridicule Nagamasa-sama?! You lout!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.24,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,A fiery little one, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.88,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Did Commander Gado being ridiculed make
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.56,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the blood rise to your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:08.27,Bullet_Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? State your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:09.67,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisawa Shoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:12.78,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually just lost my partner, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.63,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:16.03,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to pair up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.33,Bullet_Main,girlie,0000,0000,0000,,I will not serve two masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:21.16,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think we could fight Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:25.75,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,more efficiently if we paired up, \Neven if only temporarily?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:31.26,Bullet_Main,girlie,0000,0000,0000,,You're suggesting we pair up \Nuntil Aldebaran is defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:44.87,Bullet_Main,girlie,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall lend you my strength \Nfor a short amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.40,Bullet_Main,girlie,0000,0000,0000,,Do with it as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:08.34,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Satomi-kun, what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.69,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I hired her as a tactician.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:17.43,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,We need a weapons specialist if \Nwe want to defeat Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:20.25,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,But did it have to be Miori \Nand Shiba Heavy Weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:20.99,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Kisara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:23.14,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you aren't aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.46,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but the Tokyo Area's in \Nreal bad shape right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:29.52,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,No one else has the resources to back you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.21,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Aldebaran's forces have started to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.79,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,When are they expected to arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:37.23,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,11 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:39.41,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,So a little more than half a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.16,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,So, Miori...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.04,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a way to defeat Aldebaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.86,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:51.51,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,This is a special bomb created \Nby our engineering division,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:52.81,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the Ekpyrotic bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.04,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,EP bomb for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.64,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,It has 20 times more power \Nthan the 500 pound bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.18,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,that the JASDF dropped on Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:04.68,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Using this, you can completely \Nannihilate Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.41,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing, Satomi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:12.36,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just hit Aldebaran with this bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.59,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,According to our engineers' analysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:18.85,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,it has to detonate within Aldebaran's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:24.87,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,It can only destroy it using the increase \Nin power from being in a sealed state.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.73,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that we're
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:30.06,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,going to have to blast a hole in \NAldebaran's ridiculously hard shell,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:32.99,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,throw the EP bomb into the \Nwound before it regenerates,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:35.95,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and activate the bomb \Nafter the wound has healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.17,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:40.68,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell are we supposed \Nto blast a hole in its shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.31,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a weapon with \Nthat kind of piercing power...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.72,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.20,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Just one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:49.57,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,that has more power and reliability \Nthan a tank cannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:53.32,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Our most powerful and final weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:54.44,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.70,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:18:59.79,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.83,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,This plan will now be known as "Rapier's Last!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.57,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,We'll abandon this post,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:08.25,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,set up a camp in the rear,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.08,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,and face Aldebaran from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.39,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,The rear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:13.84,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a place to set up an encampment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:20.78,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,The final battle will be at \Nthe Flames of Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.97,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to find Aldebaran \Nwith those lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:31.98,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. This plan hinges on \Nhow fast we can find the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.36,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,We're just waiting for the batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:37.15,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Right. We've asked the JASDF for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:39.22,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're transporting \Nthem by land as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.22,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:45.32,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,They're taking too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:47.07,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting into our positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.87,Bullet_Main,civs,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.94,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Enju? It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:56.13,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro, do you remember the last time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.57,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,we came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.76,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking... This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:12.05,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro, I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.26,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Why does the Stolen Generation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:18.36,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,do such terrible things to the Cursed Children?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:23.27,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,We just want a place in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.33,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone says that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.39,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the civil officer system is just a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:31.08,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,good way for the Gastrea and \Nus to kill each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.87,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,A good way to get rid of the trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:34.58,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.84,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,is that what you think, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:39.64,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that working for a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:42.83,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,civil security agency is a job where I can risk
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:45.22,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,my life for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you want to believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:50.41,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:55.02,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro! Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.32,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:01.20,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju, you don't have to decide right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:04.59,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,But... in order for you to have
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:08.25,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the time to truly decide whether \Nthis world is worth saving or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:11.04,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,we need the world to keep existing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.03,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:17.17,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:18.52,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:20.59,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,Commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:22.82,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone's in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:23.72,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:27.72,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that you finally have all the cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:29.44,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,King.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:30.85,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:32.20,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:33.85,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,jack,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.23,Bullet_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:36.97,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,and joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.88,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,The adjuvant of five pairs \Nthat I originally had in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.56,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,has finally coalesced in the eleventh hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:48.77,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,All the preparations have \Nbeen made, Aldebaran!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:10.85,Bullet_Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,These are all of the batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:16.04,Bullet_Main,jerkface,0000,0000,0000,,This will mean the end of Satomi Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:39.14,Bullet_Next_Ep_Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,#13 The Ones Who Aspired to Be Gods
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.87,0:23:31.63,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,We will now eliminate the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.62,Bullet_Main,mask,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... This is war.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:34.31,Bullet_Main,tina(?),0000,0000,0000,,Target confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:35.51,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:36.49,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:38.63,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju... This is goodbye.
